window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p><b>2011 Odyssey Honor for Excellence in Audiobook Production</b></p> <p>One cold night, in a most unlikely corner of Chicago, Will Grayson crosses paths with...Will Grayson. Two teens with the same name, running in two very different circles, suddenly find their lives going in new and unexpected directions, and culminating in epic turns-of-heart and the most fabulous musical ever to grace the high school stage.&nbsp;</p> <p>Told in alternating voices from two YA superstars, this collaborative novel features a double helping of the heart and humor that have won them both legions of fans.</p>"; 
